        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>The green trailer lighting cable used with the above Models may sag onto the frame or deckplates
                    resulting in cable wear. To remedy cable wear, a shorter trailer lighting cable and a means to
                    support the cable have been implemented in production.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
